title: Test Drive Unlimited [PC Version]
description:
Great graphics. Realistic Distances. All cars and even some bikes.

// Required
- Daemon Tools
- YASU (included)
- SERIAL (included)

// Install
- Mount image with daemon
- Install
- Run YASU
- Enter serial NKEM-Q25E-LAUZ-4W3T
- Play

// Notes
- Don\&#039;t update, because the update will detect YASU and you can\&#039;t run TDU after update.
- Can\&#039;t use Multiplayer, because you will need update.
- Run Yasu everytime when you want to play TDU and you have rebooted your pc.
